Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,總會想起一些沒用的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 定春
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙去哪裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
