Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是文字燒 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,還漆黑一片 定春救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,定春 我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,都是多虧了你 謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,定春
